UnitLiquidationManager::constructor
├── when vaultManager is zero address
│   └── it reverts
├── when stabilityPool is zero address
│   └── it reverts
└── when all params are valid
    ├── it sets vaultManager
    └── it sets stabilityPool


UnitLiquidationManager::isLiquidatable
├── when vault has no debt
│   └── it returns false
├── when health factor equals exactly 1e18
│   └── it returns false
└── when health factor is below 1e18
    └── it returns true


UnitLiquidationManager::liquidate
├── when vault is not liquidatable
│   └── it reverts with LiquidationManager_VaultNotLiquidatable
└── when vault is liquidatable
    ├── when stabilityPool has enough deposits
    │   ├── it calls stabilityPool.offset with full debt and collateral
    │   └── it emits LiquidatedViaStabilityPool
    └── when stabilityPool has insufficient deposits
        ├── when liquidator has insufficient LPUSD allowance
        │   └── it reverts with LiquidationManager_InsufficientAllowance
        ├── when collateral value exceeds debt
        │   ├── it pulls LPUSD from liquidator
        │   ├── it sends debt-value LP plus 10% bonus to liquidator
        │   ├── it returns excess collateral to vault owner
        │   └── it emits LiquidatedExternally
        ├── when collateral is capped
        │   ├── it sends all collateral to liquidator
        │   └── it returns zero to vault owner
        └── when collateral value is less than debt
            ├── it sends all collateral to liquidator
            └── it emits LiquidatedExternally with zero collateralReturned
